<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span>أَنه يقْضى إِن دخل بِلَا سَبَب<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>وَمُقَابِله لَا يقْضى<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span>وَلَا تجب تَسْوِيَة فِي<a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
